What copyright notice to put on each file in SALOME sources.

a) For new file being added, choose beetween of one of these files:
- CEA_EDF.txt
- EDF.txt
- CEA.txt
and put appropriate year(s) in the first line of the header.

CEA/EDF modules:
  ATOMGEN
  ATOMIC
  ATOMSOLV
  BLSURFPLUGIN
  CALCULATOR
  COMPONENT
  CONFIGURATION
  DOCUMENTATION
  GDE
  GEOM
  GHS3DPLUGIN
  GHS3DPRLPLUGIN
  GUI
  HELLO
  HEXABLOCK
  HEXABLOCKPLUGIN
  HOMARD
  HYBRIDPLUGIN
  HexoticPLUGIN
  JOBMANAGER
  KERNEL
  LIBBATCH
  MEDCOUPLING
  MED
  NETGENPLUGIN
  PARAVIS
  PYCALCULATOR
  PYHELLO
  SAMPLES
  SHAPER
  SMESH
  TUTORIAL
  XDATA
  YACS

EDF modules:
  ADAO
  EFICAS
  GENERICSOLVER
  GMSHPLUGIN
  HYDRO
  PARAMETRIC
  YACSGEN

CEA modules:
  URANIE

OPEN CASCADE modules:
  ACISPLUGIN
  CANRECPLUGIN
  DXFPLUGIN
  LIGHT
  PYLIGHT
  RANDOMIZER
  SIERPINSKY
  XTPLUGIN

b) For existing file:

- Normally, there is already a copyright notice in the file's header, so developers have nothing to do.
- Copyrights are regularly updated (once a year) to change the date of the licence within dedicated procedure.
